data.description: Welcome to Sherwood! This is an amazing move-in ready home with three bedrooms and two full baths. The home features 1,565 sq feet with an office/play room off the kitchen and a concrete patio prefect for outdoor entertaining around a fire pit. The front door opens to an open floor plan with a family room that flows right into the kitchen. The kitchen island will certainly become your favorite gathering place. The three bedrooms are located down the hall to the left. The main bedrooms is at the end of the hall with one full bath. The second full bath is across the hall from bedrooms 2 and 3.On the opposite side of the kitchen is a play room/office/den/craft room/second family room.
